customItems.name: Heart rate / breathing rate
customItems.description: Calculates the ratio between heart rate and breathing rate in each interval. The units is beats per minute divided by breaths per minute, i.e., beats/breaths. Uses TymeBreathRate from Tymewear. Needs to be changed if this is not where your respiration data are found (e.g. "respiration").
